{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775848614206,"sessionID":"ses_2872cbdf2ffeNfm0fRDYNTyMOv","part":{"id":"prt_d78d35f41001oa9pkDBBk5rtmh","messageID":"msg_d78d35260001TOU86ERblSoNYr","sessionID":"ses_2872cbdf2ffeNfm0fRDYNTyMOv","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_c6e8c0c40a964007a82cf21a","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/pkg/router/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/pkg/router/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-010 — Router 会话管理\n2: \n3: - **AR ID**: AR-010\n4: - **Module**: `pkg/router`\n5: - **Language**: Go\n6: - **Size**: M\n7: - **Status**: Draft\n8: \n9: ## 1. 概述\n10: \n11: `pkg/router` 是 agentcube 的 HTTP 反向代理核心模块，负责将外部 HTTP 请求路由到后端的 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 实例。本设计文档聚焦于**会话管理**（Session Management）功能，基于已有的反向代理能力，增加对会话生命周期、状态追踪、JWT 认证和动态服务发现的支持。\n12: \n13: ### 1.1 目标\n14: \n15: - 实现基于 Kubernetes CRD 的动态后端服务发现\n16: - 支持会话生命周期管理（创建、更新、销毁）\n17: - 提供 JWT 令牌认证和授权\n18: - 集成 client-go 进行 Kubernetes API 交互\n19: - 提供可观测性（Prometheus 指标、健康检查）\n20: \n21: ### 1.2 依赖\n22: \n23: - `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go` — Kubernetes typed client\n24: - `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/client/informers` — Shared informer\n25: - `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/client/listers` — Resource listers\n26: - `k8s.io/client-go/kubernetes` — Kubernetes clientset\n27: \n28: ---\n29: \n30: ## 2. 架构设计\n31: \n32: ### 2.1 整体架构\n33: \n34: ```\n35: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n36: │                            Client Requests                               │\n37: └─────────────────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────────────┘\n38:                                   │\n39:                                   ▼\n40: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n41: │                         Router Server (pkg/router)                       │\n42: │  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐    │\n43: │  │  Auth       │→ │  Rate Limit │→ │  Route      │→ │   Proxy     │    │\n44: │  │  Middleware │  │  Middleware  │  │  Handler    │  │   Handler   │    │\n45: │  └─────────────┘  └─────────────┘  └─────────────┘  └─────────────┘    │\n46: │         │                 │                │                │           │\n47: │  ┌──────▼─────────────────▼────────────────▼────────────────▼──────┐   │\n48: │  │                     Backend Pool Manager                         │   │\n49: │  └────────────────────────────┬────────────────────────────────────┘   │\n50: └───────────────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────────────┘\n51:                                 │\n52:         ┌───────────────────────┼───────────────────────┐\n53:         │                       │                       │\n54:         ▼                       ▼                       ▼\n55: ┌───────────────┐      ┌─────────────────┐     ┌────────────────┐\n56: │   Health      │      │   Kubernetes    │     │    Metrics     │\n57: │   Checker     │      │   Informer      │     │    Collector   │\n58: └───────────────┘      └────────┬────────┘     └────────────────┘\n59:                                 │\n60:                                 ▼\n61:                  ┌─────────────────────────────┐\n62:                  │   Kubernetes API Server    │\n63:                  │  ┌─────────────────────┐  │\n64:                  │  │ AgentRuntime CRs     │  │\n65:                  │  │ CodeInterpreter CRs │  │\n66:                  │  └─────────────────────┘  │\n67:                  └─────────────────────────────┘\n68: ```\n69: \n70: ### 2.2 核心组件\n71: \n72: | 组件 | 职责 |\n73: |------|------|\n74: | `Router` | HTTP 服务器生命周期管理、主路由入口 |\n75: | `BackendPool` | 后端服务实例池管理、健康状态追踪 |\n76: | `RouteHandler` | 请求路径解析与目标后端选择 |\n77: | `ProxyHandler` | HTTP/WebSocket 请求转发 |\n78: | `HealthChecker` | 后端健康检查、故障检测 |\n79: | `Informer` | Kubernetes CRD 监听、动态服务发现 |\n80: | `Authenticator` | JWT/Bearer Token 认证 |\n81: | `RateLimiter` | 请求速率限制 |\n82: | `Metrics` | Prometheus 指标采集 |\n83: \n84: ### 2.3 数据流\n85: \n86: ```\n87: 1. 客户端请求进入 Router\n88:    │\n89: 2. Authenticator 验证认证信息 (JWT/Bearer)\n90:    │\n91: 3. RateLimiter 检查速率限制\n92:    │\n93: 4. RouteHandler 解析路径，提取 namespace/resource\n94:    │\n95: 5. BackendPool 根据路径/Header 选择目标后端\n96:    │\n97: 6. HealthChecker 检查后端健康状态\n98:    │\n99: 7. ProxyHandler 转发请求到后端\n100:    │\n101: 8. Metrics 记录请求指标\n102:    │\n103: 9. 响应返回客户端\n104: ```\n105: \n106: ---\n107: \n108: ## 3. 数据结构\n109: \n110: ### 3.1 核心配置\n111: \n112: ```go\n113: // Config holds router configuration\n114: type Config struct {\n115:     // Server settings\n116:     ListenAddress       string        // Listen address (default: \":8080\")\n117:     BackendTimeout      time.Duration // Backend request timeout (default: 30s)\n118:     IdleTimeout         time.Duration // Idle connection timeout (default: 60s)\n119: \n120:     // Health check settings\n121:     HealthCheckInterval time.Duration // Health check interval (default: 10s)\n122:     HealthCheckTimeout  time.Duration // Health check timeout (default: 5s)\n123:     MaxFailures        int           // Max consecutive failures before marking unhealthy (default: 3)\n124: \n125:     // Connection pool settings\n126:     MaxConnsPerBackend  int           // Max connections per backend (default: 100)\n127: \n128:     // Rate limiting\n129:     RateLimitEnabled    bool          // Enable rate limiting (default: false)\n130:     RateLimitRPS        int           // Requests per second (default: 10)\n131:     RateLimitBurst      int           // Burst size (default: 20)\n132: \n133:     // Authentication\n134:     AuthEnabled         bool          // Enable authentication (default: false)\n135:     AuthToken           string        // Bearer token for auth\n136: \n137:     // Kubernetes integration\n138:     WatchNamespaces     []string      // Namespaces to watch (empty = all)\n139:     KubeConfigPath      string        // Path to kubeconfig (optional)\n140:     ResyncPeriod        time.Duration // Informer resync period (default: 30m)\n141: \n142:     // JWT settings\n143:     JWTEnabled         bool          // Enable JWT authentication (default: false)\n144:     JWTSecretName      string        // Kubernetes Secret name for JWT keys (default: \"agentcube-router-identity\")\n145:     JWTNamespace       string        // Secret namespace (default: \"default\")\n146:     JWTExpiration      time.Duration // Token expiration (default: 5m)\n147: }\n148: ```\n149: \n150: ### 3.2 后端服务\n151: \n152: ```go\n153: // Backend represents a backend service instance\n154: type Backend struct {\n155:     URL                 *url.URL      // Backend URL\n156:     PathPrefix          string        // Path prefix for routing\n157:     Name                string        // Backend name (for logging/metrics)\n158:     Healthy             bool          // Current health status\n159:     ConsecutiveFailures int           // Consecutive failure count\n160:     LastHealthyCheck    time.Time     // Last health check timestamp\n161:    mu                  sync.RWMutex   // Mutex for concurrent access\n162: }\n163: \n164: // BackendPool manages multiple backend instances\n165: type BackendPool struct {\n166:     backends     map[string]*Backend   // key: \"agentruntime/namespace/name\" or \"codeinterpreter/namespace/name\"\n167:     headerRoutes map[string]map[string]string // header-based routing rules\n168:     defaultBackend string               // Default fallback backend\n169:     mu           sync.RWMutex\n170: }\n171: ```\n172: \n173: ### 3.3 代理上下文\n174: \n175: ```go\n176: // ProxyContext holds request context for proxying\n177: type ProxyContext struct {\n178:     Context     context.Context\n179:     Request     *http.Request\n180:     Response    http.ResponseWriter\n181:     Backend     *Backend\n182:     StartTime   time.Time\n183:     RequestID   string\n184:     Namespace   string\n185:     ResourceName string\n186:     ResourceKind string // \"agentruntime\" or \"codeinterpreter\"\n187: }\n188: ```\n189: \n190: ### 3.4 会话管理\n191: \n192: ```go\n193: // SessionInfo represents session state\n194: type SessionInfo struct {\n195:     SessionID     string            // Unique session identifier\n196:     Namespace     string            // Kubernetes namespace\n197:     ResourceName  string            // AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter name\n198:     ResourceKind  string            // \"agentruntime\" or \"codeinterpreter\"\n199:     Endpoint      string            // Backend endpoint URL\n200:     CreatedAt     time.Time         // Session creation time\n201:     LastActivity  time.Time         // Last activity timestamp\n202:     ExpiresAt     time.Time         // Session expiration time\n203:     Labels        map[string]string // Labels from CR\n204:     Status        SessionStatus     // Current status\n205: }\n206: \n207: // SessionStatus enum\n208: type SessionStatus string\n209: \n210: const (\n211:     SessionStatusPending   SessionStatus = \"Pending\"\n212:     SessionStatusActive   SessionStatus = \"Active\"\n213:     SessionStatusIdle     SessionStatus = \"Idle\"\n214:     SessionStatusExpired  SessionStatus = \"Expired\"\n215:     SessionStatusFailed   SessionStatus = \"Failed\"\n216: )\n217: ```\n218: \n219: ### 3.5 JWT 管理\n220: \n221: ```go\n222: // JWTManager handles JWT token generation and validation\n223: type JWTManager struct {\n224:     privateKey     *rsa.PrivateKey\n225:     publicKey     *rsa.PublicKey\n226:     clientset     kubernetes.Interface\n227:     secretName    string\n228:     secretNamespace string\n229:     expiration    time.Duration\n230: }\n231: \n232: // JWT claims structure\n233: type JWTClaims struct {\n234:     SessionID    string `json:\"session_id\"`\n235:     Namespace    string `json:\"namespace\"`\n236:     ResourceName string `json:\"resource_name\"`\n237:     ResourceKind string `json:\"resource_kind\"`\n238:     ExpiresAt    int64  `json:\"exp\"`\n239:     IssuedAt     int64  `json:\"iat\"`\n240:     Issuer       string `json:\"iss\"`\n241: }\n242: ```\n243: \n244: ---\n245: \n246: ## 4. API 合约\n247: \n248: ### 4.1 HTTP 端点\n249: \n250: | Method | Path | Middleware | Handler |\n251: |--------|------|------------|---------|\n252: | GET | `/health/live` | none | `handleHealthLive` |\n253: | GET | `/health/ready` | none | `handleHealthReady` |\n254: | GET | `/metrics` | none | Prometheus metrics |\n255: | GET | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/agent-runtimes/:name/*path` | auth, rateLimit, log | `handleAgentRuntimeProxy` |\n256: | POST | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/agent-runtimes/:name/*path` | auth, rateLimit, log | `handleAgentRuntimeProxy` |\n257: | GET | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/code-interpreters/:name/*path` | auth, rateLimit, log | `handleCodeInterpreterProxy` |\n258: | POST | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/code-interpreters/:name/*path` | auth, rateLimit, log | `handleCodeInterpreterProxy` |\n259: | WS | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/agent-runtimes/:name/ws` | auth, rateLimit, log | `handleAgentRuntimeWS` |\n260: | WS | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/code-interpreters/:name/ws` | auth, rateLimit, log | `handleCodeInterpreterWS` |\n261: \n262: ### 4.2 代理请求头\n263: \n264: | Header | 描述 |\n265: |--------|------|\n266: | `X-Request-ID` | 请求唯一标识 |\n267: | `X-Forwarded-For` | 原始客户端 IP |\n268: | `X-Forwarded-Proto` | 原始协议 (http/https) |\n269: | `X-Real-IP` | 真实客户端 IP |\n270: | `X-Target-Namespace` | 目标 Kubernetes 命名空间 |\n271: | `X-Target-Name` | 目标资源名称 |\n272: | `X-Target-Kind` | 目标资源类型 (agentruntime/codeinterpreter) |\n273: | `X-Session-ID` | 会话标识 (JWT token 中的 session_id) |\n274: \n275: ### 4.3 健康检查响应\n276: \n277: ```go\n278: // Live check\n279: {\"status\": \"alive\"}\n280: \n281: // Ready check - OK\n282: {\"status\": \"ready\"}\n283: \n284: // Ready check - Not ready\n285: {\"status\": \"not ready\", \"error\": \"informers not synced\"}\n286: \n287: // Metrics endpoint\n288: # Prometheus metrics format\n289: ```\n290: \n291: ### 4.4 错误响应\n292: \n293: ```json\n294: {\n295:   \"error\": \"error message\",\n296:   \"code\": \"ERR_CODE\",\n297:   \"requestId\": \"req-xxx\"\n298: }\n299: ```\n300: \n301: | Status Code | Description |\n302: |-------------|-------------|\n303: | 200 | Success |\n304: | 400 | Bad Request (invalid path/params) |\n305: | 401 | Unauthorized (invalid/missing token) |\n306: | 404 | Resource not found |\n307: | 429 | Too Many Requests (rate limit) |\n308: | 502 | Bad Gateway (backend error) |\n309: | 503 | Service Unavailable (circuit open/overloaded) |\n310: | 504 | Gateway Timeout (backend timeout) |\n311: \n312: ---\n313: \n314: ## 5. Kubernetes 集成\n315: \n316: ### 5.1 Informer 配置\n317: \n318: ```go\n319: // NewSharedInformerFactory creates informer factory\n320: func NewSharedInformerFactory(client versioned.Interface, resyncPeriod time.Duration) externalversions.SharedInformerFactory\n321: \n322: // Watch AgentRuntime resources\n323: factory.Runtime().V1alpha1().AgentRuntimes().Informer()\n324: \n325: // Watch CodeInterpreter resources\n326: factory.Runtime().V1alpha1().CodeInterpreters().Informer()\n327: ```\n328: \n329: ### 5.2 事件处理\n330: \n331: ```go\n332: // AgentRuntime event handlers\n333: func (i *Informer) AddAgentRuntime(obj *agentcubev1alpha1.AgentRuntime)\n334: func (i *Informer) UpdateAgentRuntime(oldObj, newObj *agentcubev1alpha1.AgentRuntime)\n335: func (i *Informer) DeleteAgentRuntime(obj *agentcubev1alpha1.AgentRuntime)\n336: \n337: // CodeInterpreter event handlers\n338: func (i *Informer) AddCodeInterpreter(obj *agentcubev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter)\n339: func (i *Informer) UpdateCodeInterpreter(oldObj, newObj *agentcubev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter)\n340: func (i *Informer) DeleteCodeInterpreter(obj *agentcubev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter)\n341: ```\n342: \n343: ### 5.3 后端注册逻辑\n344: \n345: ```\n346: AddAgentRuntime:\n347:   1. 检查 Status.Phase == \"Running\"\n348:   2. 检查 Status.Endpoint != \"\"\n349:   3. 构造 backend key: \"agentruntime/{namespace}/{name}\"\n350:   4. 从 Spec.TargetPorts 提取 PathPrefix (默认 \"/agent/\")\n351:   5. 调用 BackendPool.AddBackend()\n352: \n353: UpdateAgentRuntime:\n354:   1. 如果不再 Running 或无 Endpoint，调用 RemoveBackend()\n355:   2. 否则调用 BackendPool.UpdateBackend()\n356: \n357: DeleteAgentRuntime:\n358:   1. 调用 RemoveBackend()\n359: ```\n360: \n361: ---\n362: \n363: ## 6. 错误处理\n364: \n365: ### 6.1 错误类型\n366: \n367: ```go\n368: // Error codes\n369: const (\n370:     ErrCodeBadRequest       = \"ERR_BAD_REQUEST\"\n371:     ErrCodeNotFound         = \"ERR_NOT_FOUND\"\n372:     ErrCodeUnauthorized     = \"ERR_UNAUTHORIZED\"\n373:     ErrCodeTargetNotReady   = \"ERR_TARGET_NOT_READY\"\n374:     ErrCodeProxyFailed      = \"ERR_PROXY_FAILED\"\n375:     ErrCodeTimeout          = \"ERR_TIMEOUT\"\n376:     ErrCodeCircuitOpen      = \"ERR_CIRCUIT_OPEN\"\n377:     ErrCodeRateLimited      = \"ERR_RATE_LIMITED\"\n378:     ErrCodeInternalError    = \"ERR_INTERNAL\"\n379: )\n380: \n381: // RouterError represents a router-specific error\n382: type RouterError struct {\n383:     Code       string\n384:     Message    string\n385:     StatusCode int\n386:     Err        error\n387: }\n388: ```\n389: \n390: ### 6.2 错误处理策略\n391: \n392: | 错误场景 | 处理策略 |\n393: |----------|----------|\n394: | 认证失败 | 返回 401，记录错误指标 |\n395: | 资源不存在 (404) | 返回 404，不重试 |\n396: | 速率超限 | 返回 429，提示客户端退避 |\n397: | 后端超时 | 记录失败，重试一次，失败则熔断 |\n398: | 后端连接失败 | 熔断计数，达到阈值后标记不健康 |\n399: | 熔断器开启 | 返回 503，定期尝试恢复 |\n400: | 内部错误 | 返回 500，记录错误日志 |\n401: \n402: ### 6.3 日志规范\n403: \n404: ```go\n405: // Structured logging with fields\n406: log.Info(\"Request processed\",\n407:     \"requestId\", requestID,\n408:     \"method\", method,\n409:     \"path\", path,\n410:     \"namespace\", namespace,\n411:     \"resourceName\", resourceName,\n412:     \"backend\", backendName,\n413:     \"latency\", latency,\n414:     \"statusCode\", statusCode,\n415: )\n416: ```\n417: \n418: ---\n419: \n420: ## 7. 测试策略\n421: \n422: ### 7.1 单元测试\n423: \n424: | 模块 | 测试重点 |\n425: |------|----------|\n426: | `BackendPool` | 并发安全、路由选择、健康状态管理 |\n427: | `RouteHandler` | 路径解析、Header 路由、后端选择 |\n428: | `ProxyHandler` | URL 重写、Header 设置、连接池管理 |\n429: | `HealthChecker` | 健康检查触发、状态转换、失败计数 |\n430: | `Authenticator` | Token 验证、Middleware 流程 |\n431: | `RateLimiter` | 速率限制、并发安全、Middleware 流程 |\n432: | `Metrics` | 指标记录、标签正确性 |\n433: \n434: ### 7.2 集成测试\n435: \n436: ```go\n437: // 使用 fake client-go 进行集成测试\n438: import (\n439:     \"k8s.io/client-go/kubernetes/fake\"\n440:     \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go/clientset/versioned/fake\"\n441: )\n442: \n443: func TestRouterWithFakeClients(t *testing.T) {\n444:     // Setup fake clients\n445:     kubeClient := fake.NewSimpleClientset()\n446:     runtimeClient := clientsetfake.NewSimpleClientset()\n447: \n448:     // Create informer factory\n449:     informerFactory := externalversions.NewSharedInformerFactory(runtimeClient, 30*time.Minute)\n450: \n451:     // Create router with fake clients\n452:     router := NewRouter(&Config{\n453:         WatchNamespaces: []string{\"default\"},\n454:     })\n455: \n456:     // Add test AgentRuntime\n457:     ar := &agentcubev1alpha1.AgentRuntime{\n458:         ObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{\n459:             Name:      \"test-runtime\",\n460:             Namespace: \"default\",\n461:         },\n462:         Status: agentcubev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeStatus{\n463:             Phase:    agentcubev1alpha1.PhaseRunning,\n464:             Endpoint: \"http://localhost:8081\",\n465:         },\n466:     }\n467:     runtimeClient.AgentRuntimeV1alpha1().AgentRuntimes(\"default\").Create(context.Background(), ar, metav1.CreateOptions{})\n468: \n469:     // Start informers\n470:     informerFactory.Start(nil)\n471:     informerFactory.WaitForCacheSync(nil)\n472: \n473:     // Test proxy flow\n474:     req := httptest.NewRequest(\"GET\", \"/v1/namespaces/default/agent-runtimes/test-runtime/api\", nil)\n475:     w := httptest.NewRecorder()\n476:     router.ServeHTTP(w, req)\n477: \n478:     assert.Equal(t, http.StatusOK, w.Code)\n479: }\n480: ```\n481: \n482: ### 7.3 测试场景\n483: \n484: | 场景 | 预期结果 |\n485: |------|----------|\n486: | 正常代理流程 | 请求成功转发，后端响应正确返回 |\n487: | 后端动态添加 | Informer 事件触发，后端自动加入路由 |\n488: | 后端动态删除 | Informer 事件触发，后端从路由移除 |\n489: | 健康检查失败 | 连续失败 3 次后标记为不健康，流量切换 |\n490: | 认证失败 | 返回 401，请求不转发 |\n491: | 速率超限 | 返回 429，请求不转发 |\n492: | 后端超时 | 重试一次，失败返回 504 |\n493: | WebSocket 连接 | 长连接保持，双向通信正常 |\n494: \n495: ### 7.4 测试覆盖率目标\n496: \n497: | 组件 | 目标覆盖率 |\n498: |------|-----------|\n499: | server.go | 80% |\n500: | backend.go | 85% |\n501: | route.go | 85% |\n502: | proxy.go | 80% |\n503: | health.go | 85% |\n504: | informer.go | 80% |\n505: | auth.go | 90% |\n506: | ratelimit.go | 90% |\n507: | metrics.go | 85% |\n508: \n509: ---\n510: \n511: ## 8. 关键接口定义\n512: \n513: ### 8.1 Router 接口\n514: \n515: ```go\n516: type Router interface {\n517:     // Start begins serving HTTP requests\n518:     Start() error\n519: \n520:     // Stop gracefully shuts down the router\n521:     Stop(ctx context.Context) error\n522: \n523:     // AddBackend adds a backend to the pool\n524:     AddBackend(key, endpoint, pathPrefix, name string) error\n525: \n526:     // RemoveBackend removes a backend from the pool\n527:     RemoveBackend(key string)\n528: \n529:     // GetConfig returns current configuration\n530:     GetConfig() *Config\n531: \n532:     // GetMetrics returns current metrics\n533:     GetMetrics() *Metrics\n534: }\n535: ```\n536: \n537: ### 8.2 ServiceDiscoverer 接口\n538: \n539: ```go\n540: type ServiceDiscoverer interface {\n541:     // Start starts the informer\n542:     Start() error\n543: \n544:     // Stop stops the informer\n545:     Stop()\n546: \n547:     // GetEndpoint returns endpoint for given namespace and name\n548:     GetEndpoint(namespace, name, kind string) (string, error)\n549: }\n550: ```\n551: \n552: ### 8.3 ProxyHandler 接口\n553: \n554: ```go\n555: type ProxyHandler interface {\n556:     // ServeHTTP proxies the request to backend\n557:     ServeHTTP(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request, backend *Backend)\n558: \n559:     // GetTransport returns the underlying HTTP transport\n560:     GetTransport() *http.Transport\n561: }\n562: ```\n563: \n564: ---\n565: \n566: ## 9. 监控指标\n567: \n568: ### 9.1 Prometheus 指标\n569: \n570: | Metric | Type | Labels | Description |\n571: |--------|------|--------|-------------|\n572: | `router_request_duration_seconds` | Histogram | method, path, backend | Request duration |\n573: | `router_backend_requests_total` | Counter | backend, status | Backend request count |\n574: | `router_backend_healthy` | Gauge | backend | Backend health status (1/0) |\n575: | `router_errors_total` | Counter | type | Error count by type |\n576: | `router_rate_limit_rejected_total` | Counter | client_ip | Rate limited requests |\n577: | `router_active_connections` | Gauge | backend | Active connections per backend |\n578: | `router_informer_sync_total` | Counter | resource_type | Informer sync count |\n579: \n580: ### 9.2 健康检查端点\n581: \n582: - `/health/live` — Liveness probe (always returns 200 if process is running)\n583: - `/health/ready` — Readiness probe (returns 200 only if informers are synced and backend pool is initialized)\n584: \n585: ---\n586: \n587: ## 10. 实施计划\n588: \n589: ### Phase 1: 核心功能\n590: - [ ] 完善 Router 主结构\n591: - [ ] 实现 BackendPool 的线程安全操作\n592: - [ ] 实现基础代理转发\n593: \n594: ### Phase 2: Kubernetes 集成\n595: - [ ] 实现 Informer 完整功能\n596: - [ ] 集成 client-go 进行 CRD 监听\n597: - [ ] 实现 Add/Update/Delete 事件处理\n598: \n599: ### Phase 3: 会话管理\n600: - [ ] 实现 JWT Token 生成和验证\n601: - [ ] 实现会话状态追踪\n602: - [ ] 实现基于 session 的路由\n603: \n604: ### Phase 4: 可靠性\n605: - [ ] 完善健康检查逻辑\n606: - [ ] 实现熔断机制\n607: - [ ] 添加超时控制\n608: \n609: ### Phase 5: 可观测性\n610: - [ ] 完善日志结构化\n611: - [ ] 添加完整 Prometheus 指标\n612: - [ ] 实现健康检查端点\n613: \n614: ---\n615: \n616: ## 11. 依赖\n617: \n618: ### 11.1 外部依赖\n619: \n620: | Package | Version | Purpose |\n621: |---------|---------|---------|\n622: | `github.com/gin-gonic/gin` | ^1.9.0 | HTTP framework |\n623: | `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5` | ^5.0.0 | JWT token handling |\n624: | `github.com/prometheus/client_golang/prometheus` | ^1.16.0 | Metrics |\n625: | `golang.org/x/time/rate` | ^0.5.0 | Rate limiting |\n626: | `k8s.io/client-go` | ^0.34.0 | Kubernetes client |\n627: | `k8s.io/apimachinery` | ^0.34.0 | API types |\n628: | `k8s.io/klog/v2` | ^2.100.0 | Logging |\n629: \n630: ### 11.2 内部依赖\n631: \n632: | Module | Purpose |\n633: |--------|---------|\n634: | `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go` | Generated Kubernetes typed client |\n635: | `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` | CRD types |\n636: | `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/client/listers` | Resource listers |\n637: | `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/client/informers` | Shared informers |\n638: \n639: ---\n640: \n641: ## 12. 参考\n642: \n643: - [AR-009: Router HTTP 反向代理核心](design.md)\n644: - [Session Routing Design](session-routing/design.md)\n645: - [client-go library](deployment/client-go.md)\n646: - [Kubernetes Informer Pattern](https://medium.com/@cloud_eng/kubernetes-informers-the-magic-behind-operator-frameworks-2c4e3a87a9c3)\n\n(End of file - total 646 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-010 — Router 会话管理\n\n- **AR ID**: AR-010\n- **Module**: `pkg/router`\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: M\n- **Status**: Draft\n\n## 1. 概述\n\n`pkg/router` 是 agentcube 的 HTTP 反向代理核心模块，负责将外部 HTTP 请求路由到后端的 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 实例。本设计文档聚焦于**会话管理**（Session Management）功能，基于已有的反向代理能力，增加对会话生命周期、状态追踪、JWT 认证和动态服务发现的支持。\n\n### 1.1 目标\n\n- 实现基于 Kubernetes CRD 的动态后端服务发现\n- 支持会话生命周期管理（创建、更新、销毁）\n- 提供 JWT 令牌认证和授权\n- 集成 client-go 进行 Kubernetes API 交互\n- 提供可观测性（Prometheus 指标、健康检查）\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/pkg/router/design.md","time":{"start":1775848614186,"end":1775848614204}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775848614209,"sessionID":"ses_2872cbdf2ffeNfm0fRDYNTyMOv","part":{"id":"prt_d78d36415001hodktgc4jslCMA","messageID":"msg_d78d35260001TOU86ERblSoNYr","sessionID":"ses_2872cbdf2ffeNfm0fRDYNTyMOv","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_34f4ef9405574c2489c36e6c","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-010/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-010/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-010 — Router 会话管理 Tasks\n2: \n3: **Module:** pkg/router  \n4: **Language:** Go  \n5: **Size:** M  \n6: **Stage:** ST-3 (Design Completed)\n7: \n8: ---\n9: \n10: ## Phase 1: Session Configuration\n11: \n12: - [ ] **1.1** Add session config fields to `Config` struct — `SessionEnabled`, `SessionTimeout`, `SessionCookieName`, `SessionMaxActive`, `SessionCookieSecure`, `SessionCookieHTTPOnly`, `SessionCookieDomain`\n13: - [ ] **1.2** Implement `DefaultConfig()` session defaults — timeout `30m`, cookie `\"AGENTSESSIONID\"`, max `10000`, cleanup `5m`\n14: - [ ] **1.3** Add session cleanup interval config — `SessionCleanupInterval` with default `5m`\n15: \n16: ---\n17: \n18: ## Phase 2: Session Data Structures\n19: \n20: - [ ] **2.1** Create `pkg/router/session.go` — `Session` struct with ID, Backend, CreatedAt, LastActivity, ExpiresAt, Metadata fields\n21: - [ ] **2.2** Create `pkg/router/session.go` — `SessionStore` interface (Create, Get, Update, Delete, List, Cleanup)\n22: - [ ] **2.3** Implement in-memory `MemorySessionStore` — thread-safe map with RWMutex\n23: \n24: ---\n25: \n26: ## Phase 3: Session ID Generation\n27: \n28: - [ ] **3.1** Implement `GenerateSessionID()` — return UUID v4 using `github.com/google/uuid`\n29: - [ ] **3.2** Write unit test: Generate 1000 IDs, verify all unique\n30: - [ ] **3.3** Write unit test: Verify UUID v4 format\n31: \n32: ---\n33: \n34: ## Phase 4: Session Storage Operations\n35: \n36: - [ ] **4.1** Implement `SessionStore.Create()` — create session with generated ID, backend ref, timestamps\n37: - [ ] **4.2** Implement `SessionStore.Get()` — retrieve by session ID, return nil if not found\n38: - [ ] **4.3** Implement `SessionStore.Update()` — update last activity time\n39: - [ ] **4.4** Implement `SessionStore.Delete()` — remove session by ID\n40: - [ ] **4.5** Implement `SessionStore.List()` — return all active sessions\n41: - [ ] **4.6** Implement max session limit enforcement — reject new session when at limit\n42: \n43: ---\n44: \n45: ## Phase 5: Session Middleware\n46: \n47: - [ ] **5.1** Create `pkg/router/session_middleware.go` — extract session from cookie `AGENTSESSIONID`\n48: - [ ] **5.2** Create `pkg/router/session_middleware.go` — extract session from header `X-Session-ID`\n49: - [ ] **5.3** Create new session if none found — generate ID, set response cookie\n50: - [ ] **5.4** Update last activity on each request — extend expiration on activity\n51: - [ ] **5.5** Integrate middleware into router handler chain\n52: \n53: ---\n54: \n55: ## Phase 6: Session Expiration\n56: \n57: - [ ] **6.1** Implement session expiration check — mark expired based on `ExpiresAt`\n58: - [ ] **6.2** Implement sliding expiration — reset `ExpiresAt` on activity\n59: - [ ] **6.3** Reject requests with expired session — return new session\n60: \n61: ---\n62: \n63: ## Phase 7: Session Cleanup\n64: \n65: - [ ] **7.1** Implement periodic cleanup goroutine — run every cleanup interval\n66: - [ ] **7.2** Implement `Cleanup()` method — remove all expired sessions\n67: - [ ] **7.3** Add cleanup to router lifecycle — start on Start(), stop on Shutdown()\n68: - [ ] **7.4** Write unit test: Verify expired sessions are removed\n69: \n70: ---\n71: \n72: ## Phase 8: Session Affinity (Sticky Sessions)\n73: \n74: - [ ] **8.1** Store backend reference in session — on new session creation\n75: - [ ] **8.2** Route request to session's assigned backend — use stored backend key\n76: - [ ] **8.3** Handle backend removal — invalidate session when backend removed\n77: - [ ] **8.4** Write unit test: Verify same session routes to same backend\n78: \n79: ---\n80: \n81: ## Phase 9: Session Cookie Configuration\n82: \n83: - [ ] **9.1** Set cookie `Secure` flag — when `SessionCookieSecure: true`\n84: - [ ] **9.2** Set cookie `HttpOnly` flag — when `SessionCookieHTTPOnly: true`\n85: - [ ] **9.3** Set cookie `Domain` — when `SessionCookieDomain` configured\n86: - [ ] **9.4** Set cookie `Path` — default to `/`\n87: \n88: ---\n89: \n90: ## Phase 10: Session Metrics\n91: \n92: - [ ] **10.1** Add `router_sessions_active` gauge — track active session count\n93: - [ ] **10.2** Add `router_sessions_created_total` counter — track session creation\n94: - [ ] **10.3** Add `router_sessions_expired_total` counter — track expiration\n95: - [ ] **10.4** Add `router_session_duration_seconds` histogram — track session lifetime\n96: - [ ] **10.5** Update metrics on create/expire/cleanup events\n97: \n98: ---\n99: \n100: ## Phase 11: Graceful Shutdown\n101: \n102: - [ ] **11.1** Stop accepting new sessions on shutdown\n103: - [ ] **11.2** Wait for cleanup goroutine to finish\n104: - [ ] **11.3** Ensure existing sessions remain available during shutdown\n105: \n106: ---\n107: \n108: ## Phase 12: Verification\n109: \n110: - [ ] **12.1** `go build ./pkg/router/...` — successful compilation\n111: - [ ] **12.2** `go test ./pkg/router/... -v` — all unit tests pass\n112: - [ ] **12.3** Test: Default session config creates store with correct defaults\n113: - [ ] **12.4** Test: Custom session config overrides defaults\n114: - [ ] **12.5** Test: Session middleware extracts from cookie\n115: - [ ] **12.6** Test: Session middleware extracts from header\n116: - [ ] **12.7** Test: New session sets response cookie\n117: - [ ] **12.8** Test: Sticky session routes to same backend\n118: - [ ] **12.9** Test: Session expires after timeout\n119: - [ ] **12.10** Test: Cleanup removes expired sessions\n120: - [ ] **12.11** Test: Metrics reflect session state changes\n121: \n122: ---\n123: \n124: ## Dependencies\n125: \n126: - `github.com/google/uuid` — Session ID generation\n127: - `github.com/prometheus/client_golang/prometheus` — Metrics\n128: - AR-009 (completed) — Router core infrastructure\n129: \n130: ---\n131: \n132: ## References\n133: \n134: - Delta Spec: `changes/AR-010/delta-spec.md`\n135: - Design: `pkg/router/design.md`\n\n(End of file - total 135 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-010 — Router 会话管理 Tasks\n\n**Module:** pkg/router  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** M  \n**Stage:** ST-3 (Design Completed)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Session Configuration\n\n- [ ] **1.1** Add session config fields to `Config` struct — `SessionEnabled`, `SessionTimeout`, `SessionCookieName`, `SessionMaxActive`, `SessionCookieSecure`, `SessionCookieHTTPOnly`, `SessionCookieDomain`\n- [ ] **1.2** Implement `DefaultConfig()` session defaults — timeout `30m`, cookie `\"AGENTSESSIONID\"`, max `10000`, cleanup `5m`\n- [ ] **1.3** Add session cleanup interval config — `SessionCleanupInterval` with default `5m`\n\n---\n\n## Phase 2: Session Data Structures\n\n- [ ] **2.1** Create `pkg/router/session.go` — `Session` struct with ID, Backend, CreatedAt, LastActivity, ExpiresAt, Metadata fields","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-010/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775848614189,"end":1775848614207}}}}
