{"type":"text","timestamp":1775849062382,"sessionID":"ses_2872cbdf2ffeNfm0fRDYNTyMOv","part":{"id":"prt_d78da300e001t7jzy3E45AU5Zr","messageID":"msg_d78da09be001NJSWBQSlitQyYI","sessionID":"ses_2872cbdf2ffeNfm0fRDYNTyMOv","type":"text","text":"Implementation complete. Summary:\n\n**Files created:**\n- `pkg/router/session.go` - Session struct, SessionStore interface, MemorySessionStore implementation\n- `pkg/router/session_middleware.go` - Session middleware, session handler for REST API\n- `pkg/router/session_test.go` - 19 unit tests covering all session functionality\n\n**Files modified:**\n- `pkg/router/config.go` - Added session config fields\n- `pkg/router/server.go` - Integrated session management into Router\n- `pkg/router/metrics.go` - Added session metrics (active, created, expired, duration)\n\n**Key features implemented:**\n1. Session ID generation using UUID v4\n2. In-memory session store with thread-safe operations\n3. Session middleware extracting from cookie/header, creating new sessions\n4. Sliding session expiration\n5. Periodic cleanup goroutine\n6. Sticky session routing (backend stored in session)\n7. Cookie configuration (Secure, HttpOnly, Domain, Path)\n8. Session metrics for Prometheus\n9. Graceful shutdown handling","time":{"start":1775849062380,"end":1775849062380}}}
